<div class="summary">
    <div class="content-l content-l__main">
        <h1>Your summary</h1>
        <p class="lead">Buying a home is more complicated than simply trading a rent payment for a mortgage payment.  Owning a home is a long-term financial commitment that carries costs, risks, and benefits.  Examine your summary below to decide whether or not you are ready to continue working towards buying a home.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="summary-chart"></div>
    
    <div class="content-l content-l__main">
        <div class="content-l_col content-l_col-1-2">
            <section class="summary-goals">
              <header class="summary-header goals-header">
                  <h2 class="h3"><span class="cf-icon cf-icon-approved-round"></span> Goals</h2>
              </header>
                  {{> summarySection this.goals.[0]}}
                  {{> summarySection this.goals.[1]}}
                  {{> summarySection this.goals.[2]}}
            </section>
        </div>
        <div class="content-l_col content-l_col-1-2">
            
            <section class="summary-flags">
              <header class="summary-header flags-header">
                  <h2 class="h3"><span class="cf-icon cf-icon-complaint-round"></span> Red Flags</h2>
              </header>
                  {{> summarySection this.flags.[0]}}
                  {{> summarySection this.flags.[1]}}
            </section>
            
            
            <section class="summary-risks block block__padded-top">
              <header class="summary-header risks-header">
                  <h2 class="h3"><span class="cf-icon cf-icon-error-round"></span> Risks</h2>
              </header>
                  {{> summarySection this.risks.[2]}}
                  {{> summarySection this.risks.[1]}}
            </section>
            
        </div>
    </div>
    
</div>